post.description:
Use this API to create a payout from an account. 

Below fields are mandatory
```javascript
{
    "accountId": "{{accountId}}",
    "contactId": "{{contactId}}",
    "amount": "200"
}
```

***status*** field in response can have below values.
- declined
- settled
